386
00:20:39,990 --> 00:20:41,910
to girls' comics since then.

387
00:20:41,910 --> 00:20:43,230
It's you

388
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:44,590
who never left me

389
00:20:44,590 --> 00:20:46,190
