00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:02,550
It can be said

396
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:04,030
that without you,

397
00:21:04,030 --> 00:21:05,430
there wouldn't be the Mr. Meng Ye

398
00:21:05,430 --> 00:21:07,470
